---
lang: en
permalink: /offer/tailgate-toolbox/
title: Tailgate Toolbox
description: Tailgate-mounted storage boxes - additional storage space and better cargo organization in your pickup.
category: Tailgate Toolbox
---

<section class="pt-xlarge pb-xlarge products-category">
<div class="container">
  {% set breadcrumbHome = "Strona główna" %}
  {% set breadcrumbOffer = "Oferta" %}
  {% set breadcrumbOfferUrl = "/oferta/" %}
  {% if lang == "en" %}
  {% set breadcrumbHome = "Home" %}
  {% set breadcrumbOffer = "Offer" %}
  {% set breadcrumbOfferUrl = "/offer/" %}
  {% endif %}
  <nav class="breadcrumbs uppercase small color-accent-1">
    <a href="{{ langPrefix }}/">{{ breadcrumbHome }}</a>
    <span>|</span>
    <a href="{{ langPrefix }}{{ breadcrumbOfferUrl }}">{{ breadcrumbOffer }}</a>
    <span>|</span>
    <span>{{ title }}</span>
  </nav>
  <h1 class="xl split-lines color-light-1 mb-5 mt-3">{{ title }}</h1>

  {% set products = collections.productCategories[lang][category] | sortByOrder %}

  {% if products and products.length %}
    <div class="products-grid row g-3">
      {% for product in products %}
      <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-3">
        <a href="{{ product.url | url }}">
        <article class="product-card rounded-md">
          {% productImage product.data.productImage, product.data.title %}
          <div class="product-card-content p-4 bg-light-1">
          <h3 class="h4 mt-0 line-clamp-3">{{ product.data.title }}</h3>
          <a href="{{ product.url | url }}" class="color-accent-1 small">Zobacz więcej &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        </a>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  {% else %}
    <p>Brak produktów w tej kategorii.</p>
  {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>


<section class="cat-description pt-medium pb-large" id="opis">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cat-desc-content bg-light-1 p-3 p-md-5 rounded-md">
      <div class="row g-5">
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <div class="description-content">
<p>The box can also serve as a practical mini table or bar – perfect for picnics or cooking in the field. Thick seals effectively protect the interior from dust and rain, keeping tools and equipment clean and dry.</p> <div class="line-x"></div> <p>Additional features such as an integrated license plate holder, a rear-view camera mount, and pre-drilled holes for a flag pole and additional brake lights allow for full vehicle customization tailored to off-road use.</p> <div class="line-x"></div> <p>The 60-liter cargo space has been ergonomically divided into three sections, allowing for organized storage of jerry cans, tow ropes, or recovery kits. A lock with a dust cover enhances security and durability, while the non-invasive installation preserves the vehicle’s structural integrity.</p>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
         <div class="sticky">
          <div class="swiper swiper-category">
            <div class="swiper-wrapper"> {% for post in collections.works | byLang(lang) %} <div class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="work-card bg-light-1 rounded-md">
                  <a href="{{ post.data.thumbnail | url }}" class="glightbox work-image-wrap rounded-md" data-gallery="portfolio" data-no-swup>
                    <svg class="img-wrapper-icon" width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5">
                      <polyline points="8.25 2.75,2.75 2.75,2.75 13.25,13.25 13.25" />
                      <path d="m13.25 2.75-5.5 5.5m3-6.5h3.5v3.5" />
                    </svg> {% workImage "src/" + post.data.thumbnail, post.data.title %} </a>
                </div>
              </div> {% endfor %} </div>
          </div>
          <button class="magnetic swiper-gal swiper-button-prev fade-in" data-strength="60" tabindex="0" aria-label="Previous slide">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 61 61" width="61" height="61" fill="none">
              <circle cx="30.5" cy="30.5" r="30" stroke="var(--color-dark-2)"></circle>
              <path d="M34.5 24L27 31.5L34.5 39" stroke-width="2" stroke="var(--color-dark-2)"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <button class="magnetic swiper-gal swiper-button-next fade-in" data-strength="60" tabindex="0" aria-label="Next slide">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 61 61" width="61" height="61" fill="none">
              <circle cx="30.5" cy="30.5" r="30" stroke="var(--color-dark-2)"></circle>
              <path d="M28 24L35.5 31.5L28 39" stroke-width="2" stroke="var(--color-dark-2)"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="fade-in">
            <div class="swiper-scrollbar bg-light-2"></div>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <video poster="/content/products/video/poster/skrzynki-na-klape.png" controls autoplay loop muted playsinline class="mt-5 rounded-md">
        <source src="/content/products/video/skrzynki-na-tylna-klape.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>











